data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! This 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2 car garage pool home is just beautiful. With over 2,100 square feet of living area, this home is perfect for the Florida lifestyle. When you enter the home, you will be greeted by your Florida room to the left with dining availability and your master bedroom plus a guest bedroom to the right. The master bedroom features his and her closets and sliding glass doors that have a view of the pool. The master bathroom is welcoming with granite countertops and a frameless glass shower door. Head over to the center of the home to a kitchen that is truly its heart, boasting a massive kitchen island, wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and a water filtration system for fresh drinking water. The kitchen also features lighting under the cabinets, beautiful hardware, updated light fixtures, and tile back-splash. Enjoy entertaining friends and family in the kitchen with this open floor plan, looking out into the family room. It is here, where you will find your real wood burning fireplace that is perfect for cool winter nights and an absolute bonus for the holiday season. Continue through the home and you will find bedrooms three and four. These bedrooms share the updated hall/guest bathroom which also offers granite countertops and a frame-less glass shower door. Out back, in your private fenced yard, you will find a Florida oasis. Enjoy your over-sized, screened-in, swimming pool surrounded by brick pavers. This pool also has a self-feeding chlorine system, which makes maintenance easy. This home has so much to offer like, six installed security cameras, new laminate flooring in bedrooms, crown molding, water softener system, newer dishwasher, and so much more. This home is less than a minute drive to US 19 and a straight drive down County Line Road to the Suncoast Expressway. This gives you convenient access to shopping, restaurants, hospitals, Tampa International Airport, and even award winning beaches. Come live your best Florida life. Welcome home.
